Task Overview [id=task_list]
-------------

Lianne: Welcome to the team, everyone. Over the next 45 to 60 minutes, you'll work together to complete these tasks.

Lianne: First, you'll brainstorm causes for high school dropout. Then you'll review community focus group data we've collected.

Lianne: After that, you'll reflect on whether this is truly an interdisciplinary problem, and review relevant literature from different fields.

